Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西怪怪的  我不知为啥有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视中正在播放的  是跟我一点关系都没有的同县选手的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥我正支持着正处于落后的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又不知为啥觉得差不多春日要搞点事出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点整全员在车站前集合  老老实实地过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连一句话都没说上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你说带东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳装  还有足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一定要骑自行车来  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像又知道春日打算要说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说  是感觉之前好像出现过完全相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的「既视感」么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虚！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿点干劲出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  全都到齐了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要有夏天的样子  不能不做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的时间可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就要行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个只有一次的高一的暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我们是用自行车去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也骑来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行车只有你和我的两辆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  准备好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可能好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  可不能输给古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  接下来是要玩啊  你怎么就筋疲力尽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的错啊  谁的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这消毒液的气味  真给人一种实在的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  来游泳吧  比赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就读不懂这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧过来  水温温的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来挺欢乐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很欢乐的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得  凉宫同学也学会了有常识性的娱乐方法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那么开心的凉宫同学  是不会做什么震动这个世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:04:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  大概是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春以来发生了种种事情的缘故  只是变得有点神经质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们也去游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是市民泳池  倒是个更适合平民泳池这名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这种景象以前也见到过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥觉得长门好像有些无聊的样子  在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  然后春日跑来  说了这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个就是我的团员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么他们都会听的  所以随便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这种事也常有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既视感什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着考虑了下今后的活动计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样来度过已经所剩无几的暑假的计划表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假只剩下两周了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得还有很多事情没做呢  但时间却只剩那么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以听好了  接下来要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠有什么想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  这附近什么地方有盂兰盆会么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花汇演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是实玖瑠的强烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么阿虚  明天开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（来电  凉宫春日）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  将我的懒觉夺走的又是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是说找到盂兰盆会的会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  地点是市民运动场…的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  实玖瑠和有希都说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以接下来去买今晚要穿的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有  又找到了买一整套的话就会便宜的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也陪着来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日进了女装的大卖场之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自为朝比奈学姐和长门挑选了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后毫不客气地冲进了试衣间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们等了大约一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都伸懒腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人终于都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  是我给挑选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱  真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐  好棒  朝比奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏得能聚集起这么多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该是很久没来了  却觉得最近就来过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个楼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有你想要玩的捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去玩吧  如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那种东西有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？我给你买
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥有种受她照顾的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西由我来买就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  大丰收啊大丰收  十三条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那么多  就和实玖瑠一人只要了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  你那面具哪里搞来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来玩烟花吧  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道「吃饭只吃八分饱」这俗语吗  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  虽然极力想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情却让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位  明天是捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是SOS团内部的捉蝉大战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的虫子最多的那个人  就把团长的权力让给他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  虽说玩也没问题  你暑假作业做完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊  那样的作业有三天不就全部做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种麻烦事就得事先赶紧收拾掉  再毫无后顾之忧地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正确的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种家伙脑子这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是个让人有种「连这也是啊」的感觉的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团内部的捉蝉大战  就在这样的天气中举办了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各人都以自己的方式进行了奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说不出所料还是说啥呢  获胜者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  我们在还没搞清状况的状态下就被召集了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同样一无所知的情况下被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始在超市的门口发气球的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还以为要死了  不如说就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了  这么热的天真是辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长大叔也谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在实玖瑠的份上说送给我们当作工钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就为了这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  你想什么时候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我许可的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  夺去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是朝比奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有非常不好的事情…这样下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会跟朝比奈学姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有点情况  你能现在就过来么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问么！我马上就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说回不去了  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在重复同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在重复同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在重复同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  没有比现在更清楚的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才和朝比奈学姐谈了下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后意识到最近这里时间的流动出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该说是朝比奈学姐的功绩吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托她的福我也确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正无数次重复体验同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刚才就听你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说应该是八月十七日到三十一日之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正处在这永无止境的暑假的正中间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实是无止境的状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是个不会完结的Endless Summer呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个世界里  九月一日之后的时间全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐无法回到未来也是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回到不存在的未来  这是理所当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  这么莫名其妙的话哪里理所当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谁相信那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…也由我来说明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为禁止说明的事项  我一直在和未来联系和做禁止说明的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个礼拜左右没有禁止说明的事项了啊  有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正这么想着  于是禁止说明的事项…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:30.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我吓了一大跳  慌张之下就做了禁止说明的事项…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但也完全是禁止说明的事项…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐  难道说那个禁止说明的事项是放送禁止用语什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我们被困在那个叫什么封闭空间里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的时间被分割开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四时整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  全人类的记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也会重置  会从头再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是关于时间这个那个了的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  那也是没办法的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这件事和朝比奈学姐没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凉宫同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她本人没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心里什么地方总在想着暑假不要结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还留有什么遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许她是想着暑假还有什么事情剩下没做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个会把一些莫名其妙的事情\N展开到大宇宙规模的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始我就有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像乐在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近频繁发生的既视感之谜终于解开了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来  那只能理解为是由于记忆重置而散落下来的残渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都感觉得到这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只有和凉宫同学亲近的人才能感觉到这份异样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙多少有一点意识到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  别说是既视感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该有一个人保存着所有轮回中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说也该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…全都记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带问下  到底重复几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是第15499次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你在说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那话是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多的次数  我们全都在重复同样的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15499次中没有去盂兰盆会的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的这两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂兰盆会而没有捞金鱼的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9026次  其内容分成6个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了发放气球  还有搬货物  收银  发送传单  接电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了  已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15499次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门她这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上两周的话就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是594年的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长的时间仅她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够好好地保留着记忆  无数次无数次地重复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你到底到现在为止都以什么样的心情度过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又听了荒唐的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天是观测天体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是长门公寓的楼顶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天体望远镜由古泉准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春日别…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要啊  要坏掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能搞清楚的话问题也就迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试下这样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面突然抱住凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳边轻语「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这由谁来做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你没有适合的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我断然拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来做怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的了  我做这角色还不够格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会让凉宫同学增加多余的混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒涛般的暑假活动消化体制还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了打击中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了货真价实的烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加了垂钓大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有试胆大会  看连场电影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水浴  打保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及唱卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在活动来活动去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我不认为这样春日就会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此也没有什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此暑假的日子也一天天减少着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么过着  日子到了八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样课题就如实地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  还有什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假已经做了好多事了  已经很充实了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  春日  你应该还没有满足才对  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天当预备日先空下来了  大家就这样休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天再在社团教室再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  这既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还前所未有地强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样让春日回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重复了一万几千次的两星期又要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我该做什么呢  应该说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的话里应该有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  也想不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业  还没动过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎么都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重复的话  作业做了也没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天来不来  到时候就交给那时的我算啦


